    • Method Detail

      • withParameter

        public RequestParameterObfuscator.Builder withParameter(String parameter,
                                                        Obfuscator obfuscator)
        Adds a parameter to obfuscate. This method is an alias for withParameter(String, Obfuscator, CaseSensitivity) with the last specified default case sensitivity using caseSensitiveByDefault() or caseInsensitiveByDefault(). The default is CaseSensitivity.CASE_SENSITIVE.
        Parameters:
        parameter - The name of the parameter. It will be treated case sensitively.
        obfuscator - The obfuscator to use for obfuscating the parameter.
        Returns:
        This object.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - If the given parameter name or obfuscator is null.
        IllegalArgumentException - If a parameter with the same name and the same case sensitivity was already added.

      • withParameter

        public RequestParameterObfuscator.Builder withParameter(String parameter,
                                                        Obfuscator obfuscator,
                                                        CaseSensitivity caseSensitivity)
        Adds a parameter to obfuscate.
        Parameters:
        parameter - The name of the parameter.
        obfuscator - The obfuscator to use for obfuscating the parameter.
        caseSensitivity - The case sensitivity for the parameter name.
        Returns:
        This object.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - If the given parameter name, obfuscator or case sensitivity is null.
        IllegalArgumentException - If a parameter with the same name and the same case sensitivity was already added.

      • caseSensitiveByDefault

        public RequestParameterObfuscator.Builder caseSensitiveByDefault()
        Sets the default case sensitivity for new parameters to CaseSensitivity.CASE_SENSITIVE. This is the default setting.

        Note that this will not change the case sensitivity of any parameter that was already added.

        Returns:
        This object.

      • caseInsensitiveByDefault

        public RequestParameterObfuscator.Builder caseInsensitiveByDefault()
        Sets the default case sensitivity for new parameters to CaseSensitivity.CASE_INSENSITIVE.

        Note that this will not change the case sensitivity of any parameter that was already added.

        Returns:
        This object.

      • withEncoding

        public RequestParameterObfuscator.Builder withEncoding(Charset encoding)
        Sets the encoding to use. The default is StandardCharsets.UTF_8.
        Parameters:
        encoding - The encoding.
        Returns:
        This object.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - If the given encoding mode is null.
